0.1.0 - 2026-02-10

* gifmetadata tool can now write comments.
* Tool and library code now separated under main.c and gifmetadata.c respectively.
* Reworked the arguments syntax to work around stdout and stdin by default, overridable
  by providing input and output arguments.
* Makefile now compatible with BSD make.
* Complete README.
* Rewrote the CLI flag parser to be hardcoded at compile time instead of a dynamic list.
* Unified status codes.
